      "writtenOn": "2026-06-12T05:07:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We added syntactic sugar to specify external dependencies in artefact form rather than Bazel label. To get those artefact resolved automagically, new plugin attributes must be used (to deduce the external repository).\n\nAnother nice feature are allowlist and overlap tests (to prevent some transitive dependencies from leaking into plugin final artefact that already shipped in gerrit.war), that you also have not got generated automagically, because ext_deps are not passed to gerrit_plugin.\n\nWithout those allowlist test you would have missed that 5 artefacts leaking into plugin shaded JAR, that already included in gerrit.war:\n\n* commons-codec:commons-codec\n* junit:junit\n* org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient\n* org.apache.httpcomponents:httpcore\n* org.slf4j:slf4j-api\n\nAfter adding plugin and ext_deps the allowlist_test and overlap_test are added automagically:\n\n```\n  $ bazelisk test plugins/\n[...]\n//plugins/aws-dynamodb-refdb:aws-dynamodb-refdb_dependency_allowlist_test (cached) PASSED in 0.2s\n//plugins/aws-dynamodb-refdb:aws-dynamodb-refdb_dependency_overlap_test (cached) PASSED in 0.2s\n```",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 20,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 23,
        "endChar": 75
      },
      "revId": "e678acb864ff65869433a7be02aca3bc9dc02b09",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
